  "response": "Combating money laundering involves multiple legal strategies and enforcement mechanisms:\n\n1. Detection Methods\n- Financial transaction monitoring\n- Suspicious activity reporting\n- Advanced digital forensic techniques\n- International cooperation between law enforcement agencies\n\n2. Legal Frameworks\n- Anti-Money Laundering (AML) regulations\n- Know Your Customer (KYC) requirements\n- Bank Secrecy Act compliance\n- International treaties and agreements\n\n3. Investigation Approaches\n- Tracing financial transactions\n- Identifying shell companies\n- Analyzing complex financial networks\n- Gathering digital and documentary evidence\n\n4. Prosecution Strategies\n- Seizure of illicit assets\n- Criminal charges against perpetrators\n- Targeting financial intermediaries\n- Implementing significant financial penalties\n\n5. Technological Tools\n- Artificial intelligence\n- Machine learning algorithms\n- Advanced data analytics\n- Blockchain tracking technologies\n\nThese approaches help authorities systematically investigate and prosecute sophisticated money laundering operations across jurisdictions.",
